msgid "Bodies"
msgstr "Comhlachtaí"

msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ainm"

msgid "People"
msgstr "Daoine"

msgid "Groups"
msgstr "Grúpaí"

msgid "About"
msgstr "Maidir"

msgid "Contact your elected representatives about the issues that matter to you"
msgstr "Déan teagmháil le do ionadaithe tofa faoi na hábhair a leagann tú"

msgid "To get started, just enter your home address."
msgstr "Chun tús, ach isteach do sheoladh baile."

msgid "Enter your address here, e.g. Kildare Street, Dublin 2, Ireland"
msgstr "Cuir isteach do sheoladh anseo, m.sh. Sráid Chill Dara, Baile Átha Cliath 2, Éire"

msgid "Search"
msgstr "Cuardach"

msgid "We need your home address to figure out what constituency you are in."
msgstr "Ní mór dúinn do sheoladh baile a dhéanamh amach cad toghlach a bhfuil tú i."
